	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=175859><span id=Administrator>Fleven of the Seven Seas</span></a><br><b><span id=Administrator>Administrator</span></b><br><span id=notbold>98 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>To add an augmentation to an item, go to any of the five adventurer's camps and look for the little &quot;birdbath&quot; on the ground.&nbsp;&nbsp;Put the existing item you want augmented and the augmentation in the birdbath and hit the Combine button.  Voila, the augmentation has been added to your existing item.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
